aws - cli - used to automated the stuff to create ec2 instances or other services

-> all of the services requires to - high management of code/scripts

- now if we have to shift from AWS to MSAzure



Here comes - Terraform - API as Code by HashiCorp

1. Create terraform scripts - it will take care - automating the resources on the aws, gcp or azure
2. Terraform will convert them depending on the cloud providers into API calls that the cloud providers understand